You would never do that.

00:00:27.693 --> 00:00:28.961
- And I know it's wrong
because it feels good.

00:00:28.961 --> 00:00:30.263
- Yeah, don't do that.

00:00:30.263 --> 00:00:31.230
- Please don't.

00:00:31.230 --> 00:00:32.398
- I like to think of my feelings

00:00:32.398 --> 00:00:34.033 align:start size:84% position:16%
